com.tedros.fxapi.presenter.model

Class TEntityModelView<E extends ITEntity>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tedros.fxapi.presenter.model.TModelView<E>
      • com.tedros.fxapi.presenter.model.TEntityModelView<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITModelView<E>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContatoModelView, DocumentoModelView, DocumentoTableView, EnderecoModelView, ExampleViewModel, PessoaModelView, ProfileViewModel, TAuthorizationTableView, TProfileModelView, TUserModelView

    public abstract class TEntityModelView<E extends ITEntity>
extends TModelView<E>
     This engine can bind all javafx property between a TEntityModelView and a 
 ITEntity, listeners are build to listen changes in the propertys and 
 set the new values in the ITEntity.
 
  Example:
  
        // The entity
        public class ExampleEntity implements ITEntity {
 
                private Long id;
                ...
                private String name;
                private BigDecimal value;
                private Date date;
                ...             
                // getters and setters
        }
 
        // The TEntityModelView
        public class ExampleEntityModelView extends TEntityModelView<ExampleEntity>{
 
                private SimpleLongProperty id;
                ...
                private SimpleStringProperty name;
                private SimpleObjectProperty<BigDecimal> value;
                private SimpleObjectProperty<Date> date;
                
 
                public ExampleEntityModelView(ExampleEntity model) {
                        super(model);
                }
                ...
                // getters and setters
        }
    Author:
    Davis Gordon
